T19:24:55.000Z","msg":"香港既大學會教，有望係未來發展方向之一"},{"pid":"dbc3d7102888857450a53ccf81e460cde3927c61","tid":784301,"uid":78235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"334之前既hku eee year 2 project已經要寫VHDL<br />\n我諗而家year 3既technical project應該都要"},{"pid":"0d55e20e32d68a950b4359f849abd1aaec9067c4","tid":784301,"uid":62821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T13:40:29.000Z","msg":"識寫<br />\n<br />\nHardware code 比較麻煩不過就直接d"},{"pid":"c12bbfa72e0ba2233a1b741e8585f74584d89ae1","tid":784301,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T05:57:42.000Z","msg":"識Verilog <br />\n不過做緊ASIC design 唔係FPGA"},{"pid":"6d5e6023f70179e0fad25b61a442fd77964c20ef","tid":784301,"uid":102296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"FPGA同verilog係兩樣完全唔同的野黎. <br />\nFPGA係一種可以改動邏輯的晶片 (field programmable gate array)<br />\nVerilog就係一種硬件描術語言 (hardware description language, HDL)<br />\n<br />\n識用FPGA唔一定識verilog<br />\n識verilog又唔一定用在FPGA上面<br />\n<br />\nverilog可以用黎<br />\n<br />\n1. 數碼邏輯設計(digital logic design), <br />\n呢個世界上所有流行的數碼邏輯設計 (design)，包括CPU, GPU, MPU, SOC 等等的設計都係用verilog. (其實都有公司用VHDL, 不過算係少數)<br />\n<br />\n2. 寫testbench去測試設計, 跟住又衍生system verilog等用黎測試設計的語言.<br />\n<br />\n3. 物理設計(physical design)階段用作描述gate / transistor 的接線.<br />\n<br />\n4. 混合信號電路設計的語言(配合AMS)<br />\n<br />\n香港好少呢方面的工, 深圳/上海/印度就好多. 例如 hi-silicon請唔少RTL designer/DV engineer識verilog<br />\n美國精通呢種language搵工唔難. 大部份semi conductor industry都會請呢類人."},{"pid":"e7dfe1827925bc0c5cb7b899c72945242eb1abd5","tid":784301,"uid":35965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d5e6023f70179e0fad25b61a442fd77964c20ef","tid":784301,"uid":102296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:14:42.000Z","msg":"FPGA同verilog係兩樣完全唔同的野黎. <br />\nFPGA係一種可以改動邏輯的晶片 (field programmable gate array)<br />\nVerilog就係一種硬件描術語言 (hardware description language, HDL)<br />\n<br />\n識用FPGA唔一定識verilog<br />\n識verilog又唔一定用在FPGA上面<br />\n<br />\nverilog可以用黎<br />\n<br />\n1. 數碼邏輯設計(digital logic design), <br />\n呢個世界上所有流行的數碼邏輯設計 (design)，包括CPU, GPU, MPU, SOC 等等的設計都係用verilog. (其實都有公司用VHDL, 不過算係少數)<br />\n<br />\n2. 寫testbench去測試設計, 跟住又衍生system verilog等用黎測試設計的語言.<br />\n<br />\n3. 物理設計(physical design)階段用作描述gate / transistor 的接線.<br />\n<br />\n4. 混合信號電路設計的語言(配合AMS)<br />\n<br />\n香港好少呢方面的工, 深圳/上海/印度就好多. 例如 hi-silicon請唔少RTL designer/DV engineer識verilog<br />\n美國精通呢種language搵工唔難. 大部份semi conductor industry都會請呢類人."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHisilicon 連埋的中間沒-"}]}